name: First 10 data - Asc. Name
query: select * from Person order by name limit 10

name: First 10 data - Desc. Name
query: select * from Person order by name desc limit 10

name: 10 data with salary lower than 25000
query: select name, salary from Person where salary < 25000 limit 10

name: 10 data with salary greater than 25000
query: select name, salary from Person where salary > 25000 limit 10
